sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant DesktopApp as Desktop Application
    participant System as System

    User->>DesktopApp: Launch Application
    DesktopApp->>System: Initialize
    System-->>DesktopApp: Provide Resources
    DesktopApp->>User: Display Interface
    User->>DesktopApp: Interact with Features
    DesktopApp->>System: Process Requests
    System-->>DesktopApp: Return Data
    DesktopApp->>User: Update Interface
    User->>DesktopApp: Close Application
    DesktopApp->>System: Terminate Session
    System-->>DesktopApp: Release Resources